Kaminuza ya gitwe ni mwe muri kamunuza  zo mu [[Rwanda]] zigisha ibyijyanye nu ubuvuzi mu mashami atanu harimo ayubuvuzi  ,uburezi n' ikoranabuhanga .

== Amateka ya" kaminuza ya Gitwe ". ==
Kaminuza ya gitwe iherereye mu ntara y' amajyepfo  mu karere ka Ruhango mu murenge wa Bweramana  ikaba yaratangiye yitwaga "Association des Parents Adventiste de Gitwe

"APAG  mu magambo y igifaransa yatangiye gukora mu mwaka w'iguhumbi na amaganacyenda mirongo icyenda ni itatu (1993)  izagufunga mu jenoside yakorewe abatutsi mu mwaka w igihumbi na amaganacyenda mirongo icyenda ni ine (1994) . Nyuma ayaje gufungura imiryango nyuma ya jenoside ya korewe abatutsi mu [[Rwanda]] mu mwaka w'igihumbi magana cyenda na mirongo icyenda n'irindwi (1997)  aho yarifite amashami abiri icyo gihe.<ref>At a glance (uog.ac.rw)</ref> Mu mwaka wa bibiri na cumi ni icyenda ministeri y<ref>Minisiteri y’Uburezi yahagaritse amashami abiri yigisha ibijyanye n’ubuvuzi muri Kaminuza ya Gitwe - IGIHE.com</ref>' ubureze yagaritse amwe mu<ref>http://www.igihe.com/amakuru/u-rwanda/article/ifungwa-ry-amashami-y-ubuvuzi-i-gitwe-mineduc-ntikeneye-kugwiza-abaganga-b</ref> mashami ya kamunuza ya Gitwe <ref>Minisiteri y’Uburezi yahagaritse amashami abiri yigisha ibijyanye n’ubuvuzi muri Kaminuza ya Gitwe - IGIHE.com</ref>.Kaminuza yagitwe ubu itanga amasomo atandukanye ku banyeshuri baybyifuza abanyamahanga cyangwa abanyarwanda <ref>https://www.ktpress.rw/2021/05/university-of-gitwe-to-reopen-as-soon-as-it-pays-salary-arrears/</ref>.

== Amasomo . ==
Kaminuza ya gitwe itanga amasomo mu mashami atanu arimo iry’Uburezi, Ikoranabuhanga, Ubuforomo, ibijyanye na Laboratwari n’Ubuvuzi. ikaba itanga impamyabumyenyi zitandukanye harimo iyi cyiciriro cya mbere cya kaminuza <ref>https://en.igihe.com/news/hec-allows-former-gitwe-students-to-join-other</ref>.

